text: Jan-Olof Wannius (born 15 May 1942) is a Swedish equestrian. He competed in the individual jumping event at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Sweden Category:Equestrians at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm
